  <identification>
    <creator type="composer">Words: Walter Chalmers Smith, 1876.
Music: 'St. Denio' or 'Joanna' or 'Palestrina'
traditional Welsh found in "Caniadau y Cyssegr" by John Roberts, 1839.
Setting: "Caniadau y Cyssegr a'r Teulu", 1878, alt.
copyright: public domain.  This score is a part of the Open Hymnal Project, 2005 Revision.</creator>
