      <encoding-date>2026-07-21</encoding-date>
    </encoding>
    <source>Music source: Episcopal Hymnal, 1940, Hymn 301.  Also in English Hymnal, 1906 Hymn 407 (page missing in my copy).
Setting from "Caniadau y Cyssegr a'r Teulu", 1878 hymn 442, alt.</source>
